item.title: By: Simon
item.dc:creator: Simon
item.description: <p>Matthew, I was telling one of the well travelled trainees at work about your Grand Tour and she recommends the following places for the Aussie leg: Byron Bay, Whitsunday Islands, Fraser Island and Mission Beach. All the names sound nice at least! Si</p>
